  "name": {
    "en": "Sautéed Green Beans with Roasted Peanuts",
    "local_name": "Bishyimbo ne Njugu"
  },
  "description": "A simple, vibrant, and crunchy side dish where fresh green beans are quickly sautéed until tender-crisp and tossed with crunchy roasted peanuts and a hint of aromatics. It's a perfect balance of texture and flavor.",
  "origin_region": "Nationwide",
