    "occasions": ["daily_meals", "family_dinners", "special_occasions", "weekend_meals"],
    "cultural_notes": "This dish is a popular homestyle preparation that showcases two readily available ingredients. Green beans are a common vegetable in local markets, and peanuts (njugu) are a ubiquitous snack and ingredient. Combining them creates a dish that is both familiar and a little special, often prepared to add variety to the everyday meal of a staple and stew."
  },
